o;鼻子剛一說完，嘴巴就迫不及待地搶着說：&ldquo;要是沒有我，主人不能吃東西，還不餓死。&rdquo;它們誰也不肯示弱，吵得面紅耳赤。只有耳朵在一旁靜靜地聽着，什麼話也沒有說。等它們吵累了，耳朵才說：&ldquo;其實啊，我們都各有各的用處，缺了誰都不行。&rdquo;　<br />\n<br />\n　　它們聽了耳朵的話，覺得它說得很有道理。從此以後，不管怎樣，它們都能和平相處，再也沒有吵架過。"},{"pid":"15cbe27a788b9fdc53cedf1aeec73cd536f1ae43","tid":463661,"uid":123138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T19:32:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>e和b都好廢 （阿仙奴）</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1aa2146ce046dbdad6120633f669fce7d26933","tid":463661,"uid":80051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T20:18:50.000Z","msg":"唔好做多咗"},{"pid":"5d3ce020001cb9db3ee642eb3d8226a6882cbdef","tid":463661,"uid":98793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T20:20:11.000Z","msg":"最廢係橫啊腸"},{"pid":"ac4a6db32392166282dc43be729496aa86df8f1f","tid":463661,"uid":55096,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T20:34:22.000Z","msg":"樓主咁多器官嚟講，條撚係咪最廢？"},{"pid":"4008b3c51437069606fa55e8d4241c59c90d39b0","tid":463661,"uid":136639,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T20:37:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主咁多器官嚟講，條撚係咪最廢？</blockquote><br />\n比你講左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}